### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:8081/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 16",
  "description": "Latest iPhone model",
  "price": 999.99,
  "stockQuantity": 100
}

### Get all products
GET http://localhost:8081/api/products

### Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/products/1

### Update product
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "description": "Updated iPhone model",
  "price": 1299.99,
  "stockQuantity": 50
}

### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/products/1

### Get product price
GET http://localhost:8081/api/products/price/1

### Update product stock
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/products/1/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 200
} 